65857e3f","tid":415002,"uid":26003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T16:11:56.000Z","msg":"影嚟睇吓有幾大"},{"pid":"da0b7d9c18fe7209e78a34b26154000a94942ea5","tid":415002,"uid":148360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T16:13:57.000Z","msg":"做多愛啦"},{"pid":"a8a21d6b3bc58a707efcbaeb59b2b8e86b02bb90","tid":415002,"uid":66395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T16:17:51.000Z","msg":"上面話sit up 果d 一係戇鳩<br />\n一係玩鳩樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51d977272b6df0f291ef99e9dde03f94761b93d8","tid":415002,"uid":78167,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T16:29:36.000Z","msg":"話做 situp 減到肚腩果D 真係 9up 當秘笈 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> resistance training 會練到你個肚實淨但唔會有效減到。<br />\n<br />\n飲食要少糖少澱粉質低油鹽, 同唔好飲太多凍野。<br />\n<br />\n運動試下每日做 burpees + mountain climbers + plank , 頭一個禮拜 burpees + climbers 各8下一set, 做完三set plank 3 分鐘, 每個禮拜加2 set &amp; 加一分鐘 (自己google 一下點做)<br />\n<br />\n想跑步同刺激D可以加插跑步, 純為減肥唔係練氣既話唔好慢跑跑長途, 搵個無乜人可以來回跑既地方, 150 米衝刺, 抖5-10秒回頭跑, 一開始跑3個來回, 兩星期加1個。<br />\n<br />\n記得熱身事前事後拉筋, 真係 feel 到唔得唔好夾硬黎。<br />\n<br />\n利申: 努力減緊"},{"pid":"001985a5ee22bc08d073db29b5b4d289a4856129","tid":415002,"uid":84918,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T16:30:51.000Z","msg":"好想要肚腩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a5fa252cf3749ee03600f399a8aeeea99540361","tid":415002,"uid":4879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T16:44:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>話做 situp 減到肚腩果D 真係 9up 當秘笈 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> resistance training 會練到你個肚實淨但唔會有效減到。<br />\n<br />\n飲食要少糖少澱粉質低油鹽, 同唔好飲太多凍野。<br />\n<br />\n運動試下每日做 burpees + mountain climbers + plank , 頭一個禮拜 burpees + climbers 各8下一set, 做完三set plank 3 分鐘, 每個禮拜加2 set &amp; 加一分鐘 (自己google 一下點做)<br />\n<br />\n想跑步同刺激D可以加插跑步, 純為減肥唔係練氣既話唔好慢跑跑長途, 搵個無乜人可以來回跑既地方, 150 米衝刺, 抖5-10秒回頭跑, 一開始跑3個來回, 兩星期加1個。<br />\n<br />\n記得熱身事前事後拉筋, 真係 feel 到唔得唔好夾硬黎。<br />\n<br />\n利申: 努力減緊</blockquote><br />\nmark底先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efef40867c79428a88a6ff539145e56986262084","tid":415002,"uid":11970,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T16:44:54.000Z","msg":"有肚腩真男人 使咩減<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}